params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. Maximum number of sessions to return. The service may return fewer than this value. If unspecified, at most 10 sessions will be returned. The maximum value is 1000; values above 1000 will be coerced to 1000.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Optional. Page token received from a previous ListSessions call. Provide this to retrieve the subsequent page. When paginating, all other parameters provided to ListSessions must match the call that provided the page token.
